(946, 23, 'b19104', 'nmap System2', '<br>Starting Nmap 6.47 ( http://nmap.org ) <br>Nmap scan report for System2 <br>Host is up (0.000011s latency).<br>Not shown: 996 closed ports<br><br><table cellpadding="10" ><tr><th>PORT</th><th>STATE</th><th>SERVICE</th><th>VULNERABILITIES</th></tr><tbody><tr><td >1 5/tcp</td><td >open</td><td >msrpc</td><td >DoS attack</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >1 1/tcp</td><td > open </td><td >rpcbind</td><td >DDoS attack</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >2 /tcp</td><td > open </td><td >smtp</td><td >directory harvest</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >8 /tcp</td><td > open </td><td >http</td><td >sql_injection</td><td></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr><td>Device type: general purpose</td></tr><tr><td>Running: HP-UX 11i</td></tr><tr><td>OS details: HP-UX 11i</td></tr></tfoot></table><tr>Nmap done: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 0.32 seconds<br>Now you can probe another system... or you can exploit the above listed vulnerabilities.<br>Use following command: use_exploit Vul-name System-name<br>', 1, 'RDS Topology', '2021-11-12 15:43:43'),
(947, 23, 'b19104', 'nmap System1', '<br>Starting Nmap 6.47 ( http://nmap.org ) <br>Nmap scan report for System1 <br>Host is up (0.000011s latency).<br>Not shown: 996 closed ports<br><br><table cellpadding="10" ><tr><th>PORT</th><th>STATE</th><th>SERVICE</th><th>VULNERABILITIES</th></tr><tbody><tr><td >2 /tcp</td><td >open</td><td >smtp</td><td >directory harvest</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >2 /tcp</td><td > open </td><td >ftp</td><td >brute force</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >1 1/tcp</td><td > open </td><td >rpcbind</td><td >DDoS attack</td><td></td></tr><tr><td >1 5/tcp</td><td > open </td><td >msrpc</td><td >DoS_attack</td><td></td></tr></tbody><tfoot><tr><td>Device type: general purpose</td></tr><tr><td>Running: Solaris</td></tr><tr><td>OS details: Solaris</td></tr></tfoot></table><tr>Nmap done: 1 IP address (1 host up) scanned in 0.32 seconds<br>Now you can probe another system... or you can exploit the above listed vulnerabilities.<br>Use following command: use_exploit Vul-name System-name<br>', 1, 'RDS Topology', '2021-11-12 15:43:52'),
